data.description: Most unique home with a Southwestern design/flow. Semi-secluded beyond long driveway, double doors lead to airy foyer w/ cathedral ceilings & oversize windows flooding in natural light. Gourmet kitchen has double oven, granite island/bar area, & office nook. Sub-zero refrigerator conveys. Laundry room w/ plentiful shelving. Sizable primary bedroom w/ sliding doors leading to back deck. En-suite w/ double sinks, soaking jetted tub, walk-in shower, bidet, etc. L-shaped walk-in closet off en-suite. The main floor's 2 additional bedrooms offer generous space w/ same mid-century appeal throughout the house. Dedicated office room w/ built-in bookshelves. More living space awaits on lower level including entertainment room, bar, 4th bedroom, full bath, & den. Full deck spans entire back of home. Nestled between the backyard & glen are trees that offer privacy. Front parking and a 3 bay garage. Backup generator, inground & fire sprinkler system all convey as-is.
